metadata.name: Schlong Society #1
metadata.description: The Schlong Society is a collection of 10,000 randomly generated NFTs, particularly made to create awareness and help people facing this rising problem Prostate and Testicular Cancer.Our Schlong NFTs possess their own unique traits and attributes, as well as have their own purpose.The sole purpose on which the Schlong Society is founded sets the basis of helping men suffering from Prostate and Testicular Cancer and assisting in the tough battle they face every day. We also recognize the unfortunate events that happened with many of us, and we couldn't survive with them alone.At that time, we need someone to help us. Therefore, we stand by those people and help them in their critical situations by donating a certain percentage of charity from our total sales.
